    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, ensuring a comfortable and reliable driving experience. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and mechanically sound. It is ready to hit the road and would make an excellent daily driver or a solid addition to any household.",
