    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This car is in great shape and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth, reliable ride that you can count on. It\u2019s a wonderful example of a well-maintained vehicle that looks sharp and performs beautifully, making it the perfect choice for someone who values quality and dependability!",
      "price": 34500.0,
